12:17.971 --> 12:20.205
It was more than
a business meeting.

12:22.041 --> 12:23.908
              Well, what was it?

12:23.910 --> 12:26.411
It was a job offer.

12:26.413 --> 12:29.280
Gabriella and some of
our former colleagues

12:29.282 --> 12:30.849
Have put together

12:30.851 --> 12:32.751
This incredible
leadership academy,

12:32.753 --> 12:35.220
Only they lost their principal
last minute,

12:35.222 --> 12:37.021
And they need someone
to fill in right away.

12:37.023 --> 12:38.523
               An academy where?

12:38.525 --> 12:40.058
In tanzania.

12:40.060 --> 12:43.428
               Tanzania, africa,
                       tanzania?

12:43.430 --> 12:46.030
     Well, that's very far away,
                       isn't it?

12:46.032 --> 12:48.333
You have no idea how heavily
this has been weighing on me.

12:48.335 --> 12:49.901
I haven't been able
to make up my mind.

12:49.903 --> 12:51.469
I mean, one minute
I think it's a great idea.

12:51.471 --> 12:54.139
The next minute--
I can't imagine leaving you,

12:54.141 --> 12:55.907
Leaving this.

12:55.909 --> 12:58.543
Look, they're asking for
a three-month commitment.

12:58.545 --> 13:00.311
And I know, right now,
that that feels like

13:00.313 --> 13:02.547
A lifetime when we're just
starting to lay the foundation

13:02.549 --> 13:04.149
Of our life together.

13:04.151 --> 13:05.150
              Just three months?

13:05.152 --> 13:06.284
Just three months,

13:06.286 --> 13:07.786
And then I'd--
I'd come right back,

13:07.788 --> 13:10.188
If you'll have me.

13:10.190 --> 13:12.290
                     Oh, I mean,
              you have to do it.

13:12.292 --> 13:15.059
  It's a great chance to let you
             pursue your dreams.

13:15.061 --> 13:16.895
                    I'll be here
             when you come back.

13:16.897 --> 13:18.096
        I mean, I won't be here.

13:18.098 --> 13:19.297
            I'll be in my house.

13:19.299 --> 13:20.431
           With more clothes on.

13:20.433 --> 13:22.100
              I don't even think
               this is on right.

13:24.270 --> 13:26.304
I'd like to
propose a toast.

13:26.306 --> 13:28.840
To quite simply the finest woman
I have ever known.

13:28.842 --> 13:33.378
           And less importantly,
           but worth mentioning,

13:33.380 --> 13:36.080
        To will not being right.

13:38.150 --> 13:40.018
      Look at this, andy.

13:40.020 --> 13:41.452
           - Mm-hmm.
         - Almost done.

13:41.454 --> 13:43.354
    What has taken you weeks
           not to do

13:43.356 --> 13:45.423
      Was done in one day
          by a child.

13:45.425 --> 13:46.958
Speedy little fellow,
aren't you?

13:46.960 --> 13:50.295
  Well, I actually can't believe
                how easy it was.

13:50.297 --> 13:52.897
    Of course, I am an excellent
         follower of directions,

13:52.899 --> 13:55.433
           An excellent follower
                     in general.

13:55.435 --> 13:57.302
            (laurie)
 well, maybe you can teach andy
        a thing or two.

13:57.304 --> 13:58.903
      He can't seem to put
       anything together

13:58.905 --> 14:00.071
       Except an <i> excuse.</i>

14:00.073 --> 14:01.573
           [chuckles]

14:01.575 --> 14:04.275
      I just peed my pants
     emphasizing that word.

14:04.277 --> 14:07.145
     I hate my whole life.

14:07.147 --> 14:09.347
            Man, you got to feel
                     for laurie,

14:09.349 --> 14:12.150
              Hitching her wagon
            to someone like you?

14:12.152 --> 14:14.018
All right, I didn't want it
to come to this,

14:14.020 --> 14:15.420
But you leave me no choice.

14:15.422 --> 14:17.121
I'm gonna let you in
on a little secret.

14:17.123 --> 14:19.557
This isn't just
an unfinished nursery.

14:19.559 --> 14:21.292
It's much more than that.

14:26.866 --> 14:28.433
    It's a pop-up man cave.

14:28.435 --> 14:30.134
         And the sooner
     we get this work done,

14:30.136 --> 14:31.336
   The sooner I get to losing

14:31.338 --> 14:34.038
   This tiny, beautiful oasis
          of solitude

14:34.040 --> 14:35.607
  Amidst this house of chaos.

14:35.609 --> 14:38.543
                      Wow. Andy.

14:38.545 --> 14:41.079
         I'm actually impressed.

14:41.081 --> 14:43.615
           [munching]

14:43.617 --> 14:45.316
         You should be.

14:45.318 --> 14:47.485
So he <i> was</i> lying.

14:47.487 --> 14:49.888
I was right.
Just admit it.

14:49.890 --> 14:51.589
                    You weren't.
   You were, at best, wrong-ish.

14:51.591 --> 14:54.392
              This beautiful man
       was faced with a dilemma.

14:54.394 --> 14:57.328
  And plant the seed of learning
                    in tanzania,

14:57.330 --> 14:58.663
                 Or does he stay
                     and nurture

14:58.665 --> 15:01.132
           The delicate seedling
                    of our love?

15:01.134 --> 15:03.902
Ugh, that may be
the single barf-iest sentence

15:03.904 --> 15:04.969
Ever uttered.

15:04.971 --> 15:06.037
                   You're wrong,

15:06.039 --> 15:08.139
              And you just can't
                   get that fact

15:08.141 --> 15:09.674
             Through your thick,
                    swollen head

15:09.676 --> 15:12.277
                      Of frankly
          deeply overrated hair.

15:12.279 --> 15:14.045
Don't you think
for a moment

15:14.047 --> 15:17.181
That you, in fact, are the one
who's not seeing the truth?

15:17.183 --> 15:19.183
