break your heart?

15:28.662 --> 15:30.461
        I'm a nonviolent person,
            but I would like you

15:30.463 --> 15:32.196
      To imagine me slapping you
                     really hard

15:32.198 --> 15:33.431
      Across the face right now.

15:33.433 --> 15:36.234
Just don't come crying to me
when I'm right.

15:43.208 --> 15:45.944
Look, I knew having a girlfriend
would be labor-intensive,

15:45.946 --> 15:48.279
