how expensive it would be.

15:48.281 --> 15:49.280
           Oh, tell me about it.

15:49.282 --> 15:50.348
   That's why I didn't even have

15:50.350 --> 15:51.516
  A girlfriend in middle school.

15:51.518 --> 15:53.518
