this little secret of ours

16:04.431 --> 16:07.065
For, say...

16:07.067 --> 16:08.199
100 bucks.

16:08.201 --> 16:09.467
             Are you kidding me?

16:09.469 --> 16:11.736
          After I empty my soul,
               share my secrets,

16:11.738 --> 16:15.073
You want this precious
little oasis of yours,

16:15.075 --> 16:16.975
And I want a stellar date
with my girlfriend.

16:16.977 --> 16:19.177
I'm sure you and me,
we can work this out.

16:19.179 --> 16:20.979
       You're a mean little guy,
                  you know that?

16:22.614 --> 16:24.415
